incident_updates.body: We schedule a new maintenance operation to treat the remaining filerz. You can follow the operation via this task : [GRA][Webhosting] - Filerz 04/01 - 11/01. Filerz on cluster 002/003/005/007 have fully completed their backup

Start time : 22/12/2021 05:00 UTC Service impact : Website slowdown on the following cluster : Cluster002 / Cluster003 / Cluster005 / Cluster006 / Cluster007 / Cluster010 / Cluster011 / Cluster012 / Cluster013 / Cluster014 / Cluster015 / Cluster017 / Cluster020 / Cluster021 / Cluster023 / Cluster025 / Cluster026 / Cluster027 / Cluster028 / Cluster029 / Cluster030 / Cluster031 Root cause : Full backup in progress following the following maintenance operation : https://web-cloud.status-ovhcloud.com/incidents/jn65btj07cy6. The backups will take place over a few days
Update Root cause : A fullbackup is in progress on the filerz causing the drop in performance

Start time : 22/12/2021 08:30 UTC Service impact : Website slowdown/unreachable on filerz30 Root cause : Unknown Scope of impact : All offers on cluster020 Ongoing actions : Our teams are currently investigating to identify the problem. We apologise for any inconvenience caused.

Ongoing actions : The problem is still being resolved by our teams. We do not have an ETA for the moment, but it seems that the incident will last a few weeks, we will come back to you as soon as an estimated date is available. We apologize for the inconvenience.
We are continuing to investigate this issue.

Start time : 15/12/2021 13:39 UTC Service impact : Due to a technical problem, we are not able to generate the stats from December 15th until an undetermined time. We will generate the missing days at the end of the incident. Ongoing actions : Our teams are doing everything necessary to resolve the incident as soon as possible. We will get back to you with more information as time goes on. Sorry for the inconvenience

Start time : 04/01/2022 23:00 UTC End time : 11/01/2022 07:00 UTC Service impact : 15 minutes downtime for webhosting/mail when the filerz is rebooting. Service improvement : This change will permit to apply a new System Memory configuration in order to dedicate memory to the kernel. After the maintenance complete, a full backup can be performed and latency can be observed for a few more days afterwards.
